<plot>In this unique, two-part set of her world-renowned master classes - captured for the first time on video-legendary teacher and bestselling author Uta Hagen shares the insights and observations that have made her America's pre-eminent authority on the art of acting. You'll watch this extraordinary talent as she works with actors to help them create a truthful physical and emotional life on stage.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?633966</url></doc>
